{"tid":2450151,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"的士業界：政府正重啟審視處理加價程序","createTime":"2021-03-17T07:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T12:47:41.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"43c201af822d252a9280322af522acccfc7ddd98","tid":2450151,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:37:36.000Z","msg":"行政會議批准巴士公司加價申請，的士業界預料於2018年提交的加價申請，亦有望獲批。的士小巴商總會理事長周國強引述運輸署表示，正重啟審視處理業界加價的程序，相信不會拖得太長時間，預料最終「落旗」可能會加3至4元，如果業界對最終獲批加幅不滿，會再申請加價。<br />\n<br />\n周國強指，本港的士收費比其他地方低，近年受到社會運動和疫情衝擊，營運成本亦不斷增加，但起錶收費滯後4年，批評當局過去一直拖延處理加價申請。 的士業界2018年9月向運輸署申請加價，建議「落旗」加6元，市區和新界的士分別增至30元和26.5元；大嶼山的士增至37元。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2383375&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=a74e0f80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383375</a>"},{"pid":"65997f03f5c333c43996c073c160b452b503c674","tid":2450151,"uid":68689,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:40:20.000Z","msg":"所有交通工具加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n失業率就繼續升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續4人限聚令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各行業2個月封一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬炒香港經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe42dc59e28f70980a5f96cc72c917a4ea851aa","tid":2450151,"uid":3481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:41:35.000Z","msg":"加囉, 唔搭DC9車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fbb03991f09a51f28932e934a3f318fedeb1f0","tid":2450151,"uid":51583,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:41:55.000Z","msg":"我贊成一百蚊起